{"tid":1960620,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[Switch]集合啦！動物森友會｜動物之森 討論區 (102) 代客開post，一次100股","createTime":"2020-04-06T09:13:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-06T16:04:21.000Z","uid":36509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"f93ce0c582fbebcd1d194d71b9e5ea143160433c","tid":1960620,"uid":36509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T09:13:07.000Z","msg":"<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">1001開post時希望可以copy埋置頂</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">置頂</span></strong>有遊戲初期常見問題/實用工具/秘技<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">參觀人哋個島必讀 &mdash;&mdash; 良好島民約章</span></strong><br />\n1. 未經同意唔好走去搖人哋棵樹／執人啲野<br />\n2. 跑步注意安全，唔好踩爛人哋啲花<br />\n3. 個袋滿左之後，唔好周地dump垃圾<br />\n4. 唔好偷人啲野，「摸」完野記得要還<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://www.nintendo.com.hk/switch/animal_crossing_new_horizons/img/hero_pc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nintendo.com.hk%2Fswitch%2Fanimal_crossing_new_horizons%2Fimg%2Fhero_pc.jpg&h=8e954f42&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">買game前你可能會想知 - </span></strong><br />\n<br />\nQ：隻game玩乜？<br />\nA：比較休閒嘅第二人生。隻game時間係跟現實時間，亦慶祝現實節日例如聖誕，復活節等等。遊戲著重你同動物森民嘅交流互動(隻隻都有自己性格)，慢慢一齊生活 了解對方 成為密友， 同埋裝飾你間屋＆島。今隻主題係無人荒島，亦新增合成元素，你要由零開始<del><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">還債</span></span></del>建設你心目中嘅理想小島。遊戲節奏比較輕鬆，預你日日開來玩一陣，啱玩嘅可以玩幾年都得。<br />\n<br />\nQ：咩版先有中文？唔同版本可唔可以連機？<br />\nA：乜版都有中文 。可以<br />\n<br />\nQ：Online 玩咩？<br />\nA：你可以去朋友／網友嘅島度一齊開party，一齊hea，一齊砌野，一齊炒<del><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">股票</span></span></del>蘿蔔。<br />\n<br />\nQ：單機會唔會無咁好玩？<br />\nA：唔會，隻game係單機game，主要都係著重起你同動物之間嘅交流互動同埋打理你座島。不過多人連機時一樣有野玩咁解。<br />\n<br />\nQ：對手掣好靚，有無得單買？<br />\nA：暫時只見日本My Nintendo Store有得買，但係<del>唔收香港卡</del>同唔寄香港。 <strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">更新: 原來已更新可以用PayPal俾錢</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nQ：可唔可以用返以前啲Amiibo ＆ Amiibo Card？<br />\nA：可以。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZFFWQrY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZFFWQrY.png&h=8c46d7c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">圖片來源 youtube.com/watch?v=rEB1vlAiVxE</code></pre><br />\n<br />\nQ：買game實體定下載版好？有無黃店推介？<br />\nA：隻game預你日日開來玩一陣 實係下載版好，仲唔怕會益代理，真係怕唔啱玩要買實體我會建議你幫襯黃店買水貨。Read: 黃藍黑Game舖大集合 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1686000/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1686000/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nQ：同一部機唔同user save係共通？<br />\nA：無錯，一部機全部user都係住同一個島。<br />\n<br />\nQ：一機多人玩係點？<br />\nA：只有1P可以推展遊戲進度，2P只係執下素材咁。<br />\n<br />\nQ：係咪無Cloud Save？咁我壞機點算？<br />\nA：無。但官方講法係「Online會員專用壞機／唔見機時尋回save file功能開發中」 <span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">好反智</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ：係咪無得轉移個save去第二部機部度？<br />\nA：暫時無。官方講法係「動森專用 機對機save轉移功能開發中」<br />\n<br />\nQ：有咩動物村民？<br />\nA：今集總共有383個<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">好似係</span></span>。全村民「圖鑑」未有，但根據歷作會有鱷魚／食蟻獸／熊／鳥／牛／貓／雞／鹿／狗／鴨／鷹／象／蛙／羊／倉鼠／河馬／猩猩／狼／虎／松鼠／犀牛／兔／豬／企鵝／八爪魚／鴕鳥／鼠／馬騮／獅子／袋鼠／樹熊／馬... 歷代全角色(好多頁): <a href=\"https://animalcrossing.fandom.com/wiki/Category:Characters\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fanimalcrossing.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FCategory%3ACharacters&d=IFfiXVp8wSeEFxWCfbiPLWqRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=9a6861a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://animalcrossing.fandom.com/wiki/Category:Characters</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">港版特別主機(電力加強版)</span></strong> <br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>※並非數量限定商品。日後將預定再次生產</strong></span> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">-(<a href=\"https://www.nintendo.com.hk/topics/article/a_200131_02.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nintendo.com.hk%2Ftopics%2Farticle%2Fa_200131_02.html&d=IFfiXVp8wSeEFxWCfbiPLWqRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=0fa82a44\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nintendo.com.hk/topics/article/a_200131_02.html</a>)</span><br />\n預訂店鋪一覽: (官方頭盔: ※預訂及商品在庫狀況因店舖實際情況而異，詳情請向各店店員查詢)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nintendo.com.hk/hardware/switch/store/animal.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nintendo.com.hk%2Fhardware%2Fswitch%2Fstore%2Fanimal.html&d=IFfiXVp8wSeEFxWCfbiPLWqRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=ce51835b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nintendo.com.hk/hardware/switch/store/animal.html</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">入手請幫襯UNY/APITA/AEON/豐澤</span></strong> (唔經代理拎貨)<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.nintendo.com.hk/switch/animal_crossing_new_horizons/set/img/img-main-06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nintendo.com.hk%2Fswitch%2Fanimal_crossing_new_horizons%2Fset%2Fimg%2Fimg-main-06.jpg&h=56e37b2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n召集所有3DS版熟悉的面孔同新人一齊加入<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b173f30ee7556dfde5c7eca29502eb310d44e180","tid":1960620,"uid":11589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T09:14:00.000Z","msg":"重覆左兩個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f1d45d1b940927b2589fab13447f75ea3712711","tid":1960620,"uid":20756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T09:14:14.000Z","msg":"我有個個人nitendo acc add jor Friend<br />\n點樣可以係面板傾計"},{"pid":"87dc8c03d28ef6cfd8d7d8e6bf9778c54c3f5462","tid":1960620,"uid":121966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T09:14:29.000Z","msg":"屌 嚇撚死<br />\n我有隻羊無啦啦話走<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明無搞佢<br />\n想趕走個d趕唔走<br />\n<br />\n好彩有option話唔可以走 屌嚇撚死"},{"pid":"399c2069a64cd71941ea2afc92ed1d20b58d9ac7","tid":1960620,"uid":20032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T09:14:33.000Z","msg":"跪求<br />\n有無人有紅白黃白合各三<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55572b1e758f6e976919bca77645fd081ea22d12","tid":1960620,"uid":36509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T09:14:51.000Z","msg":"遊戲初期常見問題 // 實用online tools // <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n＞Android/iOS 「Nintendo Switch Online」app可以scan設計QR code，<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">連機時可以快速打字傾計</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n股價計算<br />\n<a href=\"https://mikebryant.github.io/ac-nh-turnip-prices/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmikebryant.github.io%2Fac-nh-turnip-prices%2Findex.html&d=IFfiXVp8wSeEFxWCfbiPLWqRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=649e83de\" target=\"_blank\">https://mikebryant.github.io/ac-nh-turnip-prices/index.html</a><br />\n外島攻略<br />\n<a href=\"https://wuffs.org/acnh/mysterytour.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwuffs.org%2Facnh%2Fmysterytour.html&d=IFfiXVp8wSeEFxWCfbiPLWqRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=e1a441e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://wuffs.org/acnh/mysterytour.html</a><br />\n設計任意pattern, 可生成qr code scan落遊戲度, 可以匯入任意圖片<br />\n<a href=\"https://acpatterns.com/editor\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Facpatterns.com%2Feditor&d=IFfiXVp8wSeEFxWCfbiPLWqRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=de16c6a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://acpatterns.com/editor</a><br />\n分割圖片做幾個正方形，搭上面一齊用效果更佳<br />\n<a href=\"https://pinetools.com/split-image\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpinetools.com%2Fsplit-image&d=IFfiXVp8wSeEFxWCfbiPLWqRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=8e482948\" target=\"_blank\">https://pinetools.com/split-image</a><br />\n設計主題曲<br />\n<a href=\"https://tunes.nooknet.net/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftunes.nooknet.net%2F&d=IFfiXVp8wSeEFxWCfbiPLWqRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=d36c3b84\" target=\"_blank\">https://tunes.nooknet.net/</a><br />\n<br />\nＱ：我見人地玩得好快？<br />\nＡ：隻game最主要嘅精綷係由零開始慢慢認識你啲島民(<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>記得留意島民同NPC啲對話</strong></span>)，發展同裝飾你座島，睇住座島點樣進化。最緊要啱自己play style，預左你玩幾年架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ：露營地第一隻動物係咪要硬食？<br />\nA：係<br />\n<br />\nQ：風水？<br />\nA：主人房擺唔同顏色家具增加運氣，綠 整體，紅 物品，黃 金錢。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/FRbfJgYp/fengshui.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2FFRbfJgYp%2Ffengshui.jpg&h=dc333a39&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thonky.com/animal-crossing-new-leaf/feng-shui-guide\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thonky.com%2Fanimal-crossing-new-leaf%2Ffeng-shui-guide&d=IFfiXVp8wSeEFxWCfbiPLWqRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=0f48a0d5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thonky.com/animal-crossing-new-leaf/feng-shui-guide</a><br />\n<br />\nQ：摸呀妹？<br />\nA：同館長個妹傾計有星星DIY<br />\n<br />\nQ：鐵斧頭同石斧頭有咩分別？<br />\nA：鐵會劈斷棵樹，石唔會<br />\n<br />\nQ：整爆左啲石會唔會生返？<br />\nA：第二日隨機位置生<br />\n<br />\nＱ：幾時先有得 買大頭菜(蘿蔔)，用ATM買摸過嘅野？<br />\nＡ：起商店後<br />\n<br />\nＱ：ATM有啲係非賣品？<br />\nＡ：合成物品摸完都買唔到<br />\n<br />\nＱ：點為之「摸」？<br />\nＡ：去人個島擺人地啲道具入袋之後物品圖鑑會有record，之後去返自己村部ATM可以訂嗰件貨。「摸」即係擺入袋之後再還返俾人<br />\n<br />\nＱ：點樣加速對話？<br />\nＡ：按B/長按R<br />\n<br />\nＱ：去外島請左啲新動物過我個島要幾時先會搬過來／幾時先有新島民？<br />\nＡ：keep住玩落去，有一日去揾狸吉(Tom Nook)會叫你幫新島民起屋，做好要求就會有新人搬過來<br />\n<br />\nＱ：用遊戲內design app整嘅圖案可唔可以分享？<br />\nＡ：開左時裝鋪就可以upload上網分享俾人<br />\n<br />\nＱ：點俾禮物動物島友？<br />\nＡ：間唔中對話會有得俾你揀，而機場心意卡都可以連禮物寄俾動物，佢地會回信<br />\n<br />\nＱ：點做遊戲內好友？<br />\nＡ：首先去機場揀同好友連機，會多左個好友app，之後去加左Switch好友嘅島玩一次就可以加<br />\n<br />\nＱ：點寄家俱，衫俾其他玩家？<br />\nＡ：加左遊戲內好友起狸貓ATM網購可以直寄俾好友<br />\n<br />\nＱ：見到流星可以點？<br />\nＡ：空手㩒A(好似仲要用右菇轉視角見到個天)第二日會有星星碎片執<br />\n<br />\nＱ：掘完窿種唔到樹／發光窿唔俾我種錢袋？<br />\nＡ：要揸住個鏟先得<br />\n<br />\nＱ：花係咪可以配種？<br />\nＡ：同類花種埋一齊，淋水，側邊有機會出新色花<br />\n<br />\nＱ：落兩駛唔駛淋水？<br />\nＡ：唔駛<br />\n<br />\nＱ：點先可以經Internet去人地個島？<br />\nＡ：請人來嗰位要去機場（遊戲第二日後解放）開放你個島，同時會俾個代碼你。去人個島嗰位去機楊入代碼就得。如果加左Switch主機好友可以唔駛代碼咁開放俾好友入。需有Nintendo Switch Online會員<br />\n<br />\nＱ：去人地個島時個過場動畫有無得skip？<br />\nＡ：無<br />\n<br />\nＱ：點炒蘿蔔(大頭菜)？<br />\nＡ：星期日早上入股，平日每日留意價格，啱心水價格時賣去，去朋友島賣都得架<br />\n<br />\nQ：咁多巴絲分享作曲/畫畫QR Code係有咩用架？<br />\nA：遊戲起左office之後可以揀一段仔自製音樂做小島鈴聲。而QR Code scan返來嘅Pattern可以著落衫度，又可以鋪落地度，亦可以用作家俱設計等<br />\n<br />\nQ：無人島個地型係隨機定固定？<br />\nA：一開始會隨機gen四個俾你揀，開office後會解鎖整理地型功能<br />\n<br />\nQ：一個島可以有幾多個動物村民？<br />\nA：十個<br />\n<br />\nＱ：合成好慢？<br />\nＡ：撳兩下A可加速合成<br />\n<br />\nＱ：生果點種？<br />\nＡ：掘個窿，再掉個生果落去，等幾日就有收成<br />\n<br />\nＱ：地下有啲金色嘅光？<br />\nＡ：掘開佢會有錢，掉袋錢落去會種到錢樹<br />\n<br />\nＱ：幾點轉第二日？<br />\nＡ：早上五點<br />\n<br />\nＱ：點樣跑同靜靜雞行(唔想嚇親昆蟲)？<br />\nＡ：跑 &gt; B，靜靜雞行 &gt; 細力推磨菇，捉昆蟲時持網可以長按A預備<br />\n<br />\nＱ：鋪左啲畫落地下點del走佢？<br />\nＡ：Y<br />\n<br />\nＱ：點掛自製畫去牆／著畫...?<br />\nＡ：去設計app度揀幅畫<br />\n<br />\nＱ：唔夠樹枝<br />\nＡ：搖樹，同一棵樹可以多搖幾次<br />\n<br />\nＱ：石頭/礦石無晒點算？<br />\nＡ：用鏟／斧頭鋤石頭，下面有張圖係秘技<br />\n<br />\nＱ：點樣成棵樹移植去其他地方？<br />\nＡ：食完生果可以成棵樹掘起，再去第度掘個窿種<br />\n<br />\nＱ：點解石頭一劈就爆？<br />\nＡ：食左生果特效係會劈爆石頭<br />\n<br />\nＱ：點一機多人玩？<br />\nＡ：Switch要先開多個profile先，再用嗰啲profile入game做教學。之後隨時用遊戲電話app「召集村民」<br />\n<br />\nＱ：有啲氣球飄下飄下點射落來？<br />\nＡ：用丫叉<br />\n<br />\nＱ：點樣擴大個背包？<br />\nＡ：用5000miles可去狸貓ATM換「口袋整理技巧」<br />\n<br />\nＱ：點拎丫叉/鏟/杆/梯...？<br />\nＡ：玩耐啲就有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多啲捐野俾狸貓/貓頭鷹，多啲同NPC傾計<br />\n<br />\nＱ：點去「外島」／「下西洋」？<br />\nＡ：去狸貓ATM買機票之後去機場<br />\n<br />\nＱ：「外島」有咩特別？<br />\nＡ：有機會有稀有花 蟲 魚 礦石，有巴絲話毎個外島都有一個蜂巢同一件家俱(可能要搖多幾次樹)，間中會有漂流瓶<br />\n<br />\nＱ：一開始點拎多啲鐵礦石／其他素材？<br />\nＡ：2000哩數可換機票去啲素材豐富嘅島<br />\n<br />\nＱ：點釣魚？<br />\nＡ：瞄準魚頭，咬實左魚竿先拉佢上來<br />\n<br />\nＱ：有無私人儲物空間？<br />\nＡ：有樓住之後就有<br />\n<br />\nＱ：點叫醒海邊隻海鷗？點揾佢要嘅野？<br />\nＡ：同佢講多幾次野；留意沙地有野識噴水，掘開佢<br />\n<br />\nＱ：無位擺野！啲野周街放有無問題。<br />\nＡ：擺住出面先；無問題<br />\n<br />\nＱ：啲屋/設施可唔可以調位？<br />\nＡ：有office後可以<br />\n<br />\nＱ：點拎多啲礦石？<br />\nＡ：好似幅圖咁整三個窿先<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rvjEZrt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrvjEZrt.jpg&h=79ad3315&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nＱ：巴絲分享，外島捉狼蛛攻略<br />\nＡ：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ：點解跟哂方法整狼蛛島都係失敗/咁少/咁慢<br />\nA：4月開始蟲類會多左田鱉 田鱉會係河到生 但佢又計係蟲類 所以大大打擊左狼蛛刷新既機率 (解決方法係去冇河既外島)<br />\n<br />\n設計無人島<br />\n<a href=\"https://planimalcrossing.com/nh/start/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplanimalcrossing.com%2Fnh%2Fstart%2F&d=IFfiXVp8wSeEFxWCfbiPLWqRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=23b152df\" target=\"_blank\">https://planimalcrossing.com/nh/start/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12687f31bf085fb945bf681831be3bd9a18ce477","tid":1960620,"uid":3447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T09:15:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"425220bf1f1a002714f44a9132c3ff1c84854ff2","tid":1960620,"uid":278307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"399c2069a64cd71941ea2afc92ed1d20b58d9ac7","tid":1960620,"uid":20032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T09:14:33.000Z","msg":"跪求<br />\n有無人有紅白黃白合各三<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T09:15:19.000Z","msg":"我都想要百合"},{"pid":"04b29a679ea18737a6abe049eabb157372726a77","tid":1960620,"uid":11589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T09:15:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TUB6HeC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTUB6HeC.png&h=222d92a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n岩岩外島遇到佢<br />\n明明英文叫cookie<br />\n但中文叫佩琳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"h